summary: This is the calendar for any common year starting on Tuesday, January 1 .
full_text:
This is the calendar for any common year starting on Tuesday, January 1 . Examples: Gregorian years 1974, 1985, 1991, 2002, 2013, 2019, 2030, 2041, and 2047 or Julian year 1919 .
^ a b "A common year beginning on Tuesday", jonstlouis.htmlplanet.com, 2011, webpage: HTMcal.

title: Common year starting on Tuesday
